    "en": {
      "title": "Several players including Dhananjaya have 'Covid'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of Sri Lanka Cricket said that several players, including Dhananjaya de Silva, who were scheduled to participate in the second and final Test match against Australia starting tomorrow (8), have been confirmed to be infected with 'Covid'.",
        "In place of those players, hard bowlers Prabhat Jayasuriya and Lakshan Sandakan have been called to the squad.",
        "Angelo Mathews, who was previously infected with 'Covid', is currently in the squad and Praveen Jayawickrama was found to be infected earlier."
      ],
